# Slow gate, run only on push (not on every commit). Mirrors
# `pnpm verify` and the CI workflow exactly so a clean local push
# means the CI build will pass for the same reasons.
#
# Order is cheapest-first so failures fail fast:
#   1. typecheck   ~22s
#   2. unit tests  ~10s
#   3. audit       <2s (network)
#
# `set -e` is implicit in husky v9 — any non-zero exit aborts the push.
pnpm run typecheck
pnpm run test
pnpm run audit:ci
